Package com.fiorano.edbc.testlpc

Interface Summary
Bundle This class contains the messages used by the service in logging or events.
 

Class Summary
JMSHandler JMSHandler class holds the MessageProducer, MessageConsumer, InputPortHandler and session for every session on the InputPort.
JMSObjects JMSObjects handles the creation of connection parameters, does the lookup and creates the JMSHandler.
RequestProcessor Processes the input request.
TestLPC Execution class for TestLPC.
TestLPCMessageListener In order to receive message asynchronously as they are delivered to the message consumer, the client program needs to create a message listener that implements the MessageListener interface.
